String Challenge
Have the function StringChallenge(str) take the str parameter being passed and capitalize the first letter of each word. Words will be separated by only one space.
Examples
Input: "hello world"
Output: Hello World
Input: "i ran there"
Output: I Ran There


SOLVE

import java.util.*; 
import java.io.*;

class Main {

  public static String StringChallenge(String str) {
    // code goes here  
    return str;
  }

  public static void main (String[] args) {  
    // create string
    String name = "hello world";

    // create two substrings from name
    // first substring contains first letter of name
    // second substring contains remaining letters
    String firstLetter = name.substring(0, 1);
    String remainingLetters = name.substring(1, name.length());

    // change the first letter to uppercase
    firstLetter = firstLetter.toUpperCase();

    // join the two substrings
    name = firstLetter + remainingLetters;
    System.out.println("Name: " + name);

  }
}


RUN CODE

Name: Hello world
